#Text=Molossia has its own systems of measurement and dates .
#Text=Tell us about them .
#Text=Our dates are based from the year that Molossia was founded , back in 1977 , thus today is 29 April 2008 XXXI .
#Text=Founder 's Day , the day Molossia was founded , was 26 May 1977 .
#Text=Our measurement system is called the Kokintz System , named for Professor Kokintz of Grand Fenwick .
#Text=All of the units of measurement are based of things unique to Molossia .
#Text=The basic unit of length , the Norton , is based on the length of my hand .
#Text=The basic unit of volume , the Simms , is equal to a can of Diet Pepsi , my favorite drink .
#Text=The basic unit of weight , the Fenwick , is based on a tube of Cookie Dough , and the basic unit of temperature , the Zenda , is based on the height of the First Lady .
#Text=We like to keep things interesting .
#Text=Molossia also has its own time zone .
#Text=Tell us about it .
#Text=Again , to keep things interesting , we devised our own time zone , Molossian Standard Time .
#Text=It is 39 minutes ahead of Pacific Standard Time and 21 minutes behind Mountain Standard Time .
#Text=Can people visit Molossia ?
#Text=Yes , absolutely !
#Text=We love have tourists visit .
#Text=We have thus far had 14 non-family visit Molossia in the past year , our first ever arriving in spring 2007 XXX .
#Text=A visit to Molossia takes about an hour , during which I take all visitors on a tour of our country and tell them about Molossia and micronations in general .
#Text=Cookie dough is served , too , of course , and I stamp passports .
#Text=It is very important , though , that all visitors contact our government , to arrange a date and time for the visit .
#Text=Please do not show up unannounced !
#Text=Are there any tourist attractions in Molossia ?
#Text=What can a visitor see and do while in your nation ?
#Text=Yes , we do have a few sights to see .
#Text=Visitors can see Republic Square , the Peace Pole , the micronation direction sign , Norton Park , the Molossia Railroad , and the Tower of the Winds .
#Text=A visit to Molossia is always interesting , if for no other reason than it 's " the country just up the street on the right " .
#Text=Are you planning on expanding Molossia 's borders in the near future ?
#Text=We would love to do so , but I think we are about as big as we can be right now .
#Text=Of course , should our country ever had a large economic windfall , then we will certainly expand .
#Text=Molossia is one of the world 's most serious and well known micronations .
#Text=In under ten years , it has gained the attention of the media and respect of thousands .
#Text=Where do you see your country in another ten years ?
